Program: Omnibus
Title: Bullfighting
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376kd9
Last Broadcast Date: 24 June 1992
The fact that death is a real possibility is part of the reason for the revival of interest in bullfighting in Spain. A look at the appeal and practises of this Spanish tradition and also the opposition to it on the grounds of animal cruelty.